  fhir:DomainResource.text [
     fhir:Narrative.status [ fhir:value "extensions" ] ;
     fhir:Narrative.div "<div xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml\"><p class=\"res-header-id\"><b>Generated Narrative: CapabilityStatement PDSm-GestionnaireDePartageDeDocuments</b></p><a name=\"PDSm-GestionnaireDePartageDeDocuments\"> </a><a name=\"hcPDSm-GestionnaireDePartageDeDocuments\"> </a><h2 id=\"title\">CI-SIS Partage-De-Documents-De-Sante - GestionnaireDePartageDeDocuments</h2><ul><li>Implementation Guide Version: 3.1.1 </li><li>FHIR Version: 4.0.1 </li><li>Supported Formats: <code>xml</code>, <code>json</code></li><li>Published on: 2021-07-30 14:32:30+0200 </li><li>Published by: ANS </li></ul><blockquote class=\"impl-note\"><p><strong>Note to Implementers: FHIR Capabilities</strong></p><p>Any FHIR capability may be 'allowed' by the system unless explicitly marked as 'SHALL NOT'. A few items are marked as MAY in the Implementation Guide to highlight their potential relevance to the use case.</p></blockquote><h3 id=\"shallIGs\">SHALL Support the Following Implementation Guides</h3><ul><li><a href=\"index.html\">https://interop.esante.gouv.fr/ig/fhir/pdsm/ImplementationGuide/ans.fhir.fr.pdsm</a></li></ul><h2 id=\"rest\">FHIR RESTful Capabilities</h2><div class=\"panel panel-default\"><div class=\"panel-heading\"><h3 id=\"mode1\" class=\"panel-title\">Mode: <code>server</code></h3></div><div class=\"panel-body\"><div><p>Il s’agit d’un système d’information ou d’un composant d'un système d’information qui stocke, classe et archive les documents d’un dossier patient.</p>\n</div><div class=\"lead\"><em>Security</em></div><blockquote><div><p>L’ANS propose des référentiels dédiés à la politique de sécurité (la PGSSI-S ) et des mécanismes de sécurisation sont définis dans les volets de la couche Transport du Cadre d’Interopérabilité des systèmes d’information de santé (CI-SIS)</p>\n</div></blockquote><div class=\"lead\"><em>Summary of System-wide Interactions</em></div><ul><li>Supports the <code>transaction</code>interaction described as follows:<div><p>https://interop.esante.gouv.fr/ig/fhir/pdsm/StructureDefinition/pdsm-comprehensive-provide-document-bundle</p>\n</div></li></ul></div></div><h3 id=\"resourcesCap1\">Capabilities by Resource/Profile</h3><h4 id=\"resourcesSummary1\">Summary</h4><p>The summary table lists the resources that are part of this configuration, and for each resource it lists:</p><ul><li>The relevant profiles (if any)</li><li>The interactions supported by each resource (<b><span class=\"bg-info\">R</span></b>ead, <b><span class=\"bg-info\">S</span></b>earch, <b><span class=\"bg-info\">U</span></b>pdate, and <b><span class=\"bg-info\">C</span></b>reate, are always shown, while <b><span class=\"bg-info\">VR</span></b>ead, <b><span class=\"bg-info\">P</span></b>atch, <b><span class=\"bg-info\">D</span></b>elete, <b><span class=\"bg-info\">H</span></b>istory on <b><span class=\"bg-info\">I</span></b>nstance, or <b><span class=\"bg-info\">H</span></b>istory on <b><span class=\"bg-info\">T</span></b>ype are only present if at least one of the resources has support for them.</li><li><span>The required, recommended, and some optional search parameters (if any). </span></li><li>The linked resources enabled for <code>_include</code></li><li>The other resources enabled for <code>_revinclude</code></li><li>The operations on the resource (if any)</li></ul><div class=\"table-responsive\"><table class=\"table table-condensed table-hover\"><thead><tr><th><b>Resource Type</b></th><th><b>Profile</b></th><th class=\"text-center\"><b title=\"GET a resource (read interaction)\">R</b></th><th class=\"text-center\"><b title=\"GET all set of resources of the type (search interaction)\">S</b></th><th class=\"text-center\"><b title=\"PUT a new resource version (update interaction)\">U</b></th><th class=\"text-center\"><b title=\"PATCH a new resource version (patch interaction)\">P</b></th><th class=\"text-center\"><b title=\"POST a new resource (create interaction)\">C</b></th><th><b title=\"Required and recommended search parameters\">Searches</b></th><th><code><b>_include</b></code></th><th><code><b>_revinclude</b></code></th><th><b>Operations</b></th></tr></thead><tbody><tr><td><a href=\"#List1-1\">List</a></td><td><a href=\"StructureDefinition-pdsm-submissionset-comprehensive.html\">https://interop.esante.gouv.fr/ig/fhir/pdsm/StructureDefinition/pdsm-submissionset-comprehensive</a></td><td class=\"text-center\">y</td><td class=\"text-center\">y</td><td class=\"text-center\"/><td class=\"text-center\"/><td class=\"text-center\"/><td>date, DesignationType, identifier, status, PDSm_isArchived, title, SourceId, source, PDSm_authorOrg, code, PDSm_List_PatientAsSource, patient, PDSm_List_PractitionerRoleAsSource</td><td/><td/><td/></tr><tr><td><a href=\"#DocumentReference1-2\">DocumentReference</a></td><td><a href=\"StructureDefinition-pdsm-comprehensive-document-reference.html\">https://interop.esante.gouv.fr/ig/fhir/pdsm/StructureDefinition/pdsm-comprehensive-document-reference</a></td><td class=\"text-center\">y</td><td class=\"text-center\">y</td><td class=\"text-center\"/><td class=\"text-center\">y</td><td class=\"text-center\"/><td>type, setting, identifier, creation, security-label, status, PDSm_isArchived, PDSm_DocumentReference_period-start, PDSm_DocumentReference_period-end, format, category, relatesto, event, period, DocumentReference Patient, DocumentRefence Author</td><td/><td/><td/></tr><tr><td><a href=\"#Binary1-3\">Binary</a></td><td><a href=\"http://hl7.org/fhir/R4/binary.html\">http://hl7.org/fhir/StructureDefinition/Binary</a></td><td class=\"text-center\">y</td><td class=\"text-center\"/><td class=\"text-center\"/><td class=\"text-center\"/><td class=\"text-center\"/><td/><td/><td/><td/></tr></tbody></table></div><hr/><div class=\"panel panel-default\"><div class=\"panel-heading\"><h4 id=\"List1-1\" class=\"panel-title\"><span style=\"float: right;\">Resource Conformance: unspecified </span>List</h4></div><div class=\"panel-body\"><div class=\"container\"><div class=\"row\"><div class=\"col-lg-6\"><span class=\"lead\">Base System Profile</span><br/><a href=\"StructureDefinition-pdsm-submissionset-comprehensive.html\">PDSm SubmissionSet Comprehensive</a></div><div class=\"col-lg-3\"><span class=\"lead\">Profile Conformance</span><br/><b>SHALL</b></div><div class=\"col-lg-3\"><span class=\"lead\">Reference Policy</span><br/></div></div><p/><div class=\"row\"><div class=\"col-lg-6\"><span class=\"lead\">Interaction summary</span><br/><ul><li>Supports <code>read</code>, <code>search-type</code>.</li></ul></div></div><p/><div class=\"row\"><div class=\"col-lg-7\"><span class=\"lead\">Search Parameters</span><table class=\"table table-condensed table-hover\"><thead><tr><th>Conformance</th><th>Parameter</th><th>Type</th><th>Documentation</th></tr></thead><tbody><tr><td><b>SHALL</b></td><td><a href=\"http://hl7.org/fhir/R4/list.html#search\">date</a></td><td><code>date</code></td><td><div><p>Représente la date et heure de soumission.</p>\n</div></td></tr><tr><td><b>SHALL</b></td><td><a href=\"https://profiles.ihe.net/ITI/MHD/4.2.3/SearchParameter-List-DesignationType.html\">DesignationType</a></td><td><code>token</code></td><td><div><p>Représente le type d’activité associé à l’événement clinique ayant abouti à la constitution du lot de soumission.</p>\n</div></td></tr><tr><td><b>SHALL</b></td><td><a href=\"http://hl7.org/fhir/R4/list.html#search\">identifier</a></td><td><code>token</code></td><td><div><p>Représente l'identifiant.</p>\n</div></td></tr><tr><td><b>SHALL</b></td><td><a href=\"http://hl7.org/fhir/R4/list.html#search\">status</a></td><td><code>token</code></td><td><div><p>Représente le statut du lot de soumission.</p>\n</div></td></tr><tr><td><b>SHALL</b></td><td><a href=\"SearchParameter-PDSm-isArchived.html\">PDSm_isArchived</a></td><td><code>token</code></td><td><div><p>permet distinguer les lots de soumission et les fiches archivés des actifs.</p>\n</div></td></tr><tr><td><b>SHALL</b></td><td><a href=\"http://hl7.org/fhir/R4/list.html#search\">title</a></td><td><code>string</code></td><td><div><p>Représente le titre du lot de soumission.</p>\n</div></td></tr><tr><td><b>SHALL</b></td><td><a href=\"https://profiles.ihe.net/ITI/MHD/4.2.3/SearchParameter-List-SourceId.html\">SourceId</a></td><td><code>token</code></td><td><div><p>Représente l’identifiant unique global du système émetteur du lot de soumission.</p>\n</div></td></tr><tr><td><b>SHALL</b></td><td><a href=\"http://hl7.org/fhir/R4/list.html#search\">source</a></td><td><code>reference</code></td><td><div><p>Représente l’auteur du lot de soumission, quand l'auteur est de type patient, practitionerrole ou device.</p>\n</div></td></tr><tr><td><b>SHALL</b></td><td><a href=\"SearchParameter-PDSm-List-authorOrg.html\">PDSm_authorOrg</a></td><td><code>reference</code></td><td><div><p>Représente l’auteur du lot de soumission, quand l'auteur est de type organization.</p>\n</div></td></tr><tr><td><b>SHALL</b></td><td><a href=\"http://hl7.org/fhir/R4/list.html#search\">code</a></td><td><code>token</code></td><td><div><p>Représente le but du lot de soumission.</p>\n</div></td></tr><tr><td><b>SHALL</b></td><td><a href=\"SearchParameter-PDSm-List-PatientAsSource.html\">PDSm_List_PatientAsSource</a></td><td><code>reference</code></td><td><div><p>Recherche sur les éléments source:Patient.given et source:Patient.family.</p>\n</div></td></tr><tr><td><b>SHALL</b></td><td>patient</td><td><code>reference</code></td><td><div><p>Recherche sur l'élément subject restreint à la ressource Patient.</p>\n</div></td></tr><tr><td><b>SHALL</b></td><td><a href=\"SearchParameter-PDSm-List-PractitionerRoleAsSource.html\">PDSm_List_PractitionerRoleAsSource</a></td><td><code>reference</code></td><td><div><p>Recherche sur les éléments source:PractitionerRole.practitioner:Practitioner.given et source:PractitionerRole.practitioner:Practitioner.family.</p>\n</div></td></tr></tbody></table></div><div class=\"col-lg-5\"> </div></div></div></div></div><div class=\"panel panel-default\"><div class=\"panel-heading\"><h4 id=\"DocumentReference1-2\" class=\"panel-title\"><span style=\"float: right;\">Resource Conformance: unspecified </span>DocumentReference</h4></div><div class=\"panel-body\"><div class=\"container\"><div class=\"row\"><div class=\"col-lg-6\"><span class=\"lead\">Base System Profile</span><br/><a href=\"StructureDefinition-pdsm-comprehensive-document-reference.html\">PDSm Comprehensive DocumentReference</a></div><div class=\"col-lg-3\"><span class=\"lead\">Profile Conformance</span><br/><b>SHALL</b></div><div class=\"col-lg-3\"><span class=\"lead\">Reference Policy</span><br/></div></div><p/><div class=\"row\"><div class=\"col-lg-6\"><span class=\"lead\">Interaction summary</span><br/><ul><li>Supports <code>read</code>, <code>search-type</code>, <code>patch</code>.</li></ul></div></div><p/><div class=\"row\"><div class=\"col-lg-7\"><span class=\"lead\">Search Parameters</span><table class=\"table table-condensed table-hover\"><thead><tr><th>Conformance</th><th>Parameter</th><th>Type</th><th>Documentation</th></tr></thead><tbody><tr><td><b>SHALL</b></td><td><a href=\"http://hl7.org/fhir/R4/documentreference.html#search\">type</a></td><td><code>token</code></td><td><div><p>Représente le type du document.</p>\n</div></td></tr><tr><td><b>SHALL</b></td><td><a href=\"http://hl7.org/fhir/R4/documentreference.html#search\">setting</a></td><td><code>token</code></td><td><div><p>Représente le cadre d’exercice de l’acte qui a engendré la création du document</p>\n</div></td></tr><tr><td><b>SHALL</b></td><td><a href=\"http://hl7.org/fhir/R4/documentreference.html#search\">identifier</a></td><td><code>token</code></td><td><div><p>Représente l'identifiant unique d'une fiche d'un document.</p>\n</div></td></tr><tr><td><b>SHALL</b></td><td><a href=\"https://profiles.ihe.net/ITI/MHD/4.2.3/SearchParameter-DocumentReference-Creation.html\">creation</a></td><td><code>date</code></td><td><div><p>Représente la date et l'heure de la création du document.</p>\n</div></td></tr><tr><td><b>SHALL</b></td><td><a href=\"http://hl7.org/fhir/R4/documentreference.html#search\">security-label</a></td><td><code>token</code></td><td><div><p>Contient les informations définissant le niveau de confidentialité d'un document.</p>\n</div></td></tr><tr><td><b>SHALL</b></td><td><a href=\"http://hl7.org/fhir/R4/documentreference.html#search\">status</a></td><td><code>token</code></td><td><div><p>Représente le statut de la fiche d'un document.</p>\n</div></td></tr><tr><td><b>SHALL</b></td><td><a href=\"SearchParameter-PDSm-isArchived.html\">PDSm_isArchived</a></td><td><code>token</code></td><td><div><p>permet distinguer les lots de soumission et les fiches archivés des actifs.</p>\n</div></td></tr><tr><td><b>SHALL</b></td><td><a href=\"SearchParameter-PDSm-DocumentReference-period-start.html\">PDSm_DocumentReference_period-start</a></td><td><code>date</code></td><td><div><p>Représente la date de début de l’acte de référence.</p>\n</div></td></tr><tr><td><b>SHALL</b></td><td><a href=\"SearchParameter-PDSm-DocumentReference-period-end.html\">PDSm_DocumentReference_period-end</a></td><td><code>date</code></td><td><div><p>Représente la date de fin de l’acte de référence.</p>\n</div></td></tr><tr><td><b>SHALL</b></td><td><a href=\"http://hl7.org/fhir/R4/documentreference.html#search\">format</a></td><td><code>token</code></td><td><div><p>Format technique détaillé du document.</p>\n</div></td></tr><tr><td><b>SHALL</b></td><td><a href=\"http://hl7.org/fhir/R4/documentreference.html#search\">category</a></td><td><code>token</code></td><td><div><p>Représente la classe du document (compte rendu, imagerie médicale, traitement, certificat, ....).</p>\n</div></td></tr><tr><td><b>SHALL</b></td><td><a href=\"http://hl7.org/fhir/R4/documentreference.html#search\">relatesto</a></td><td><code>reference</code></td><td><div><p>Représente l'identifiant d'une association entre deux fiches.</p>\n</div></td></tr><tr><td><b>SHALL</b></td><td><a href=\"http://hl7.org/fhir/R4/documentreference.html#search\">event</a></td><td><code>token</code></td><td><div><p>Actes et pathologies en rapport avec le document.</p>\n</div></td></tr><tr><td><b>SHALL</b></td><td><a href=\"http://hl7.org/fhir/R4/documentreference.html#search\">period</a></td><td><code>date</code></td><td><div><p>Représente la période.</p>\n</div></td></tr><tr><td><b>SHALL</b></td><td><a href=\"http://hl7.org/fhir/R4/documentreference.html#search\">DocumentReference Patient</a></td><td><code>reference</code></td><td><div><p>Représente l'identifiant du patient qui est le sujet du document.</p>\n</div></td></tr><tr><td><b>SHALL</b></td><td><a href=\"http://hl7.org/fhir/R4/documentreference.html#search\">DocumentRefence Author</a></td><td><code>reference</code></td><td><div><p>Représente l'identifiant de l'auteur qui est l'auteur du document.</p>\n</div></td></tr></tbody></table></div><div class=\"col-lg-5\"> </div></div></div></div></div><div class=\"panel panel-default\"><div class=\"panel-heading\"><h4 id=\"Binary1-3\" class=\"panel-title\"><span style=\"float: right;\">Resource Conformance: unspecified </span>Binary</h4></div><div class=\"panel-body\"><div class=\"container\"><div class=\"row\"><div class=\"col-lg-6\"><span class=\"lead\">Base System Profile</span><br/><a href=\"http://hl7.org/fhir/R4/binary.html\">Binary</a></div><div class=\"col-lg-3\"><span class=\"lead\">Profile Conformance</span><br/><b>SHALL</b></div><div class=\"col-lg-3\"><span class=\"lead\">Reference Policy</span><br/></div></div><p/><div class=\"row\"><div class=\"col-lg-6\"><span class=\"lead\">Interaction summary</span><br/><ul><li>Supports <code>read</code>.</li></ul></div></div><p/></div></div></div></div>"
